nodes.text: He was on board Tansarii Point Station during some events of the Galactic Civil War. Bun'Del was slightly overweight, and was an ordinary civilian while on board the station.

Bun'Del was a non-player character in the video game Star Wars Galaxies, a massively multiplayer online-role playing game developed by Sony Online Entertainment and published by LucasArts, prior to its closure on December 15, 2011.
